html:
Signal

Enter a signal value. Make sure that the field is populated with the custom-generated signal name matching the name of the signal specified in the Which signal is generated? field of the Throw signal element (Fig. 2 and Fig. 3) in the corresponding process. Such signal name can be generated by user at random.
